{"tid":421824,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"APPLE 宣佈將macOS、iOS採用的XNU核心架構開源！","createTime":"2017-10-02T14:30:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-03T14:25:35.000Z","uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"15412807a49c3b1f870264d03c6a25d2a547a635","tid":421824,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T14:30:23.000Z","msg":"在2015年的WWDC開發者大會中宣布將旗下程式語言Swift 2.0以後版本開源之後，稍早更進一步在GitHub網站將macOS (包含以前的OS X)，以及iOS作業系統採用的類Unix核心架構XNU予以開源。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2017/10/01/draft/4067402.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=1050&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2017%2F10%2F01%2Fdraft%2F4067402.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D1050%26exp%3D3600&h=b2616b57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n相比過往給人在架構開源態度相對封閉的蘋果，近年來似乎在此方面態度有所改變，不但在WWDC 2015期間宣布將本身Swift 2.0程式語言予以開源，稍早更確定將用於macOS及iOS作業系統的類Unix核心架構XNU透過GitHub網站開源。<br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/11017/2734334\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F11017%2F2734334&d=UuZ1iPTJC%2FYJcpizRsrAQJZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=81df1604\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/11017/2734334</a></div>"},{"pid":"eb190686c7b035089dc506d1468a781d0f617384","tid":421824,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T14:37:10.000Z","msg":"XNU是一個由蘋果電腦發展的用於macOS操作系統的操作系統內核。 它是Darwin操作系統的一部分，跟隨着Darwin一同作為自由及開放原始碼軟件被發佈。 它還是iOS、tvOS和watchOS操作系統的內核。 XNU是X is Not Unix的縮寫。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://opensource.apple.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fopensource.apple.com%2F&d=UuZ1iPTJC%2FYJcpizRsrAQJZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=f393c410\" target=\"_blank\">https://opensource.apple.com/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://github.com/apple/darwin-xnu\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Fapple%2Fdarwin-xnu&d=UuZ1iPTJC%2FYJcpizRsrAQJZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=f0125738\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/apple/darwin-xnu</a>"},{"pid":"a989ae16ac9438e2e55ec74d9299bd060170b8b7","tid":421824,"uid":3032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T14:46:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c3ee5ab1affc335e1bf40a302d316243e52f808","tid":421824,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T14:51:23.000Z","msg":"即係點 想食埋m$ market?"},{"pid":"b9dcd5c885316651d7d00b5c69d60d9e3596f6f3","tid":421824,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T16:50:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>即係點 想食埋m$ market?</blockquote><br />\n食linux kernel market"},{"pid":"7d3b571faecfed4e83e8219ac21c74c3cd5912b4","tid":421824,"uid":1130,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T16:52:10.000Z","msg":"open source會唔會有咩影響"},{"pid":"ac62f87f956e54f98604c16ec6a1f91515b178e1","tid":421824,"uid":99420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T18:01:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e2e1559a5cf747f6c75822b0ab65a0fdc844f264","tid":421824,"uid":1123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T14:17:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>open source會唔會有咩影響</blockquote><br />\n你老母少左條陰毛咁囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6720e4f106359957add4cc918c8f26c70d829036","tid":421824,"uid":35542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T14:25:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>即係點 想食埋m$ market?</blockquote><br />\n食linux kernel market</blockquote><br />\n食到先好講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}